00:24:05,480 --> 00:24:08,324
MOUSE: Out of order. 
 TONY: Let me in here. Let me in.

334
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:10,164
Jeez.

335
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:12,527
You've been waiting long? 
 Great. She's been...

336
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:15,405
Come on! Other people in need here, 
 you know.

